cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper discusses deep learning-based semi-supervised learning approaches and their application to image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of adversarial examples, which suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.CL (Computation and Language).
